WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to the Strangle Escape Course
I am your safety protection instructor

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Today we will learn escape techniques for wall pinning
This is a common dangerous situation in daily life

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
First, staying calm is most important
Don't panic, observe the surrounding environment

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
When someone tries to pin you against the wall
Immediately push them away with both hands

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
At the same time, shout for help loudly
To attract attention from people around

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
If the person continues to harass
You can kick their groin area

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Remember, safety first
Don't hesitate to use any necessary means

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Now let's practice these techniques
To ensure you can protect yourself in danger
